gomodel:SYNGO_5430  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Figure 2i: \"Electron micrograph showing ghrelin immunoreactivity in dense-cored vesicles of an axon terminal.\"\n\nFigure 2j: \"Electron micrograph showing a symmetrical synaptic membrane specialization (black arrows) between a ghrelin-immunolabeled axon terminal (25 nm immunogold in dense-cored vesicles) and an unlabeled dendrite.\"\n\nFigure 2k: \"Electron microscopy revealed direct appositions between ghrelin (immuno peroxidase in dense-cored vesicles) and NPY-producing presynaptic terminals (25 nm immunogold in dense-cored vesicles).\". Experimental description: Imaging in Figure 2 was performed in mice.\nAntibody source is not mentioned, but its specificity was validated using a knockout mouse (Figure 2d)." ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2286-1587" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2514-0216" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-4973-5732" ;
        dc:date           "2023-03-16" ;
        dc:title          "SYNGO_CC_5430" ;
        pav:providedBy    "https://syngo.vu.nl" ;
        biolink:in_taxon  "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/NCBITaxon_10090" .

